Package iaik.smime.ess

Class Summary
ContentHints The S/MIMEv3 ESS ContentHints attribute.
ContentIdentifier The S/MIMEv3 ESS ContentIdentifier attribute.
ContentReference The S/MIMEv3 ESS ContentReference attribute.
EntityIdentifier The S/MIMEv3 ESS type EntityIdentifier.
EquivalentLabels The S/MIMEv3 ESS EquivalentLabels attribute.
ESSAttributeValue Groups all ESS Attribute implementations.
ESSCertID This class implements the S/MIMEv3 ESSCertID type.
ESSCertIDv2 This class implements the S/MIMEv3 ESS ESSCertIDv2 type.
ESSIssuerSerial This class implements the S/MIMEv3 ESS IssuerSerial type.
ESSSecurityLabel The S/MIMEv3 ESS ESSSecurityLabel attribute.
MLData The S/MIMEv3 ESS type MLData.
MLExpansionHistory The S/MIMEv3 ESS MLExpansionHistory attribute.
MLReceiptPolicy This class implements the S/MIMEv3 MLReceiptPolicy type.
MsgSigDigest The S/MIMEv3 ESS MsgSigDigest attribute.
Receipt The S/MIMEv3 ESS Receipt content type.
ReceiptContent This class can be used to create S/MIME messages for sending an signed receipt as response to receipt request.
ReceiptRequest The S/MIMEv3 ESS ReceiptRequest attribute.
ReceiptsFrom The S/MIMEv3 ESS type ReceiptsFrom.
SecurityCategory This class is the basic implementation for S/MIMEv3 ESS SecurityCategory values.
SigningCertificate This class implements the S/MIMEv3 SigningCertificate type.
SigningCertificateV2 This class implements the S/MIMEv3 ESS SigningCertificateV2 type.
UnknownSecurityCategory This class implements any unknown SecurityCategory value.
 

Exception Summary
ESSException This exception is thrown when there occurs a problem with S/MIME ESS.
ESSRuntimeException This exception may be thrown if there occurs an error caused at runtime.
MLExpansionHistoryOverflowException This exception is thrown when an MLExpansionHistory overflow occurs.
MLExpansionLoopException This exception may be thrown if a mail list expansion loop is detected.
SecurityLabelException This exception maybe thrown when processing an ESSSecurityLabel or EquivalentLabels attribute.
